{
  "texts": [
    "Other methods involve knowledge distillation [30], reinforcement learning [365], etc.",
    "Is there a better training method to enable GR models to master generating DocID ranking lists?",
    "For example, RLHF [36] has been effectively used to train LLMs [210,286], though at a high cost.",
    "Exploring RLHF in the GR field is also worthwhile.Model Structure.",
    "As discussed in Section 3.1.2, most current GR models are based on encoderdecoder Transformers structures [281,307,371], such as T5 [231] and BART [138]."
